"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-gymnast-suffers-nasty-cut-black-eye-scary-fall-wins-olympic-medal-21331325\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Brazilian gymnast Flavia Saraiva dusted herself off after a huge fall to win a bronze medal at theOlympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fl\\u00e1via_Saraiva\", \"score\": 0.9999999630538248, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Flavia Saraiva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fl\\u00e1via_Saraiva\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fl\\u00e1via_Saraiva\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 24-year-old was warming up on the uneven bars before the artistic gymnastics team final in theParison Tuesday when she slipped during a swing and crashed to the floor.\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Saraiva landed hard with her knee hitting her face and stayed down momentarily before she rolled out of the way to allow her teammates to continue warming up.\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Brazil's coach checked on her briefly before the medical team patched up the bleeding cut above her right eye, which was immediately swollen.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 442, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8479165735431077, \"rank\": 0.1556537337252867, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She left to get medical attention but she is back,' said Rich Lerner, a commentator for United States broadcaster NBC.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 643, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"score\": 0.9999996002473726, \"rank\": 3.9544303202564576e-07, \"text\": \"Rich\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rich_Hardbeck\"}, {\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\", \"score\": 0.999850294407886, \"rank\": 0.00014971931476766043, \"text\": \"Lerner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Jay_Lerner\"}, {\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9964374358426257, \"rank\": 0.002824765587264692, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9923475911428263, \"rank\": 0.007235320494083055, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She's tough.'\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic gold medalist Laurie Hernandez added: 'There is nothing worse than not just falling in warm-ups but blanking out and having that moment replay in your mind right before competing.'\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking about her injury, Saravia said: 'I could not see, it bled, but the team's doctor told me everything was all right.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 1034, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I believe my knee hit my eye when I tripped.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not the first time it happened to me.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are warriors.'\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After being treated by medical staff, Saravia went on to compete and did not suffer any more falls as she helped Brazil register a total score of 164.497 - which pipped Team GB to the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8479165735431077, \"rank\": 0.1556537337252867, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1313, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999998172197759, \"rank\": 1.2281115421537878e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When I realized I was on the floor, lying down with my knee in my face.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just rolled over so Rebeca could warm up,' Saraiva told Globo after the event.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I said, 'guys, where am I?'.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then Chico said, 'it's bleeding, it's bleeding'.\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chico_Marx\", \"score\": 0.9999999999515694, \"rank\": 4.3480519722055234e-11, \"text\": \"Chico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chico_Marx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chico_Marx\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I put my hand on my face and my eye was bleeding, I did not understand anything.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1657, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he asked if I was warm.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I said, 'now I am awake'.'\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"for those wondering what happenedpic.twitter.com/QyOEaOBBft  Saraiva is competing in the third Olympics of her career.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her best result before the bronze medal was fifth place on the balance beam in 2016.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The United States, led by Simone Biles, won gold with a total of 171.296.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1929, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9964374358426257, \"rank\": 0.002824765587264692, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles is now the the most decorated Olympic gymnast in United States' history with eight medals, includi